Time to get into some holiday spirits ♥️💫

It felt like a “Miracle” just being able to get dressed up with @jgwilb and spend the night out in Charlotte at the cutest holiday pop up going on now at @backstageloungeclt! Of course we had to invite our favorites and taste testers @wilberdanielle and @zbutts to give their stamp of approval for these naughty and nice cocktails! To put it simply, “that’s dangerous” were the first words from Danielle after a sip of the Jingle Balls Nog 😏.

🌟 10/10 would highly recommend the Miracle pop up to put you in a festive mood! No reservations are required ☎️ but I would absolutely get there early since it’s first come first serve!

🎥 For ordering reference the cocktail lineup includes:

🛢️Holiday Spiked Chai
🦖Grandma Got Run Over By A T-rex 
🎅Yippie Ki Yay Mother F*!
🪩 Jingle Balls Nog 

***Please drink responsibly!

Should have just slept through all of September because it was not a good one. Several setbacks, death, grieving… I’ll be glad to put this month and honestly entire summer behind me. September was teed up to be so promising with a few things I had planned, but as little mishaps started to stack up, it all came crashing down when I found out my grandpa died. It’s been exhausting so right now I’m letting my drama out, so the trauma doesn’t stay in. Thanks for letting me vent it out 🥀🫶🏻☁️

💀🥀Kicking off my Dead Inside tour by previewing Haunted by Black Lagoon at @backstageloungeclt! 

The @blacklagoonpopup features epic immersive Halloween decor, themed food, cocktails, and 💥MOCKTAILS💥 On a personal note I was honestly so excited to see & taste a wide variety of mocktails since I usually have to bring a reliable source to taste any alcoholic menu for me (or waste the drink). But this time I got to enjoy a few of the themed drinks 🖤 It’s such an appreciated addition to any drink menu. It made this popup all the more enjoyable! 

Here are the deets if you are ✨dying✨ to enter:

🪦 October 4th - October 31st
🪦 Tues-Sat | 5pm-12am
🪦 No reservations

📞Bad Witches Only
